1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,555
Stoicism is not feeling
nothing.

2
00:00:02,555 --> 00:00:05,509
It is noticing anger,
fear, and pride

3
00:00:05,509 --> 00:00:08,383
without letting them
write your next

4
00:00:08,383 --> 00:00:08,782
move.

5
00:00:08,782 --> 00:00:11,257
When provoked, take one
breath.

6
00:00:11,257 --> 00:00:14,211
Ask what the objective
is: clarity, a

7
00:00:14,211 --> 00:00:16,846
boundary, a decision,
or silence.

8
00:00:16,846 --> 00:00:19,800
Answer the objective,
not the insult.
